# ğŸ“ˆ Stock Price Prediction using LSTM (FastAPI)

This project is an **end-to-end stock price prediction system** built using **LSTM (Long Short-Term Memory)** neural networks. It is trained on the **POWERGRID stock dataset** and deployed using **FastAPI**. The application fetches real-time stock data from **Yahoo Finance API**, predicts the **next 60 days of stock prices**, and visualizes **EMA, SMA, and crossover trading signals**.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

* ğŸ”® **Next 60 Days Stock Price Prediction** using LSTM
* ğŸ“Š **Technical Indicators**:

  * Simple Moving Average (SMA)
  * Exponential Moving Average (EMA)
  * EMA/SMA Crossover Buy & Sell Signals
* ğŸŒ **Live Stock Data Fetching** from Yahoo Finance
* âš¡ **FastAPI Backend** for real-time predictions
* ğŸ“‰ **Interactive Graphs** for price trends and signals
* â¬‡ï¸ **Downloadable Prediction & Signal Graphs**
* ğŸ§  Model trained on **POWERGRID historical stock data**

